{"id": "aos032", "name": "Cam_Noah_693_08_09", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>The continuation exam is right around the corner. I'm so nervous...</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "You don't have to be nervous. According to a senior, the continuation exam from I to J is not actually that difficult.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>It's easy for you to say that, since you, Clara and Daniel are the Big 3. You guys are going to crush this exam with ease... \nIf I don't stay in the same grade range as you guys, I'm getting demoted to class 2 the next semester...</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "You worry too much~ Iris will be fine too. We studied late every day just for this, didn't we?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>Yes...</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Just approach it normally. With your current grades, you can mess up 1 or 2 questions and still end up in class 1. All you need to do is perform up to your usual standards. If you're too nervous, you won't remember what you studied.\nRelax~ We are all going to J-1, together. \n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>Got it! Hearing you say that really calms my mind down... Though I hope you can encourage yourself like that on stage too. Every time I see you on-stage, I always get sweaty palms because you're literally shaking. Haha.</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Don't tease me like that~ That's mean!\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>Aroma is about to become a celebrity... feels like you're going to another world. I'm happy for you, but I also feel a bit... lonely. When you become famous, will we still be friends?</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "You're overexaggerating... I promise you, that no matter what happens, we will always be best friends. Forever.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>Uh-huh! Deal!\nOn a side note, it's getting pretty late. Is it ok for you to stay up till now?</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Sister is not coming home tonight, so I can stay up a bit later. However, it's about time I go to sleep too.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>Yep, same for me. See you tomorrow at school then! Goodnight,</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Goodnight~\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Call ends]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Yawns~ Tuner-san, set the alarm clock. I'm going to bed.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Tuner-san]"], "content": "<i>Alarm clock set. Goodnight, Aroma~ Goodnight~</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_02", "Crashing noises"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "！？\nWhat is that noise...?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">...... Damnit!! Those pieces of s***!</font>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Noah...?\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Noah? Are you alright?\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Ah... Aroma... I just got home...\nDid I disturb your sleep...?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "No, I was just about to sleep... Are you okay? You look terrible...\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Those old bastards! Hoarding all the resources yet don't have the knowledge to do anything! what can't they just all die!?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "...... Noah!?\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "They understand nothing! The importance of this technique! This will offer a brand-new interpretation to existing technology!! Such a major breakthrough! Could anybody else achieve these results!?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Tuner-san]"], "content": "<i>Noah blood alcohol level too high, recommend proper rest.</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Shut up...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["TunerKun_off", "Tuner-san OFF"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Aroma... you understand, right? All the hard work I did...\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "I understand. It's all for sister...\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "No...... Ugh!\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "image", "attrs": ["aos3201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Woah! Be careful. Maybe you should sit down first?\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Everything I did... It's all for you...</font>\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Eh?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">IT'S ALL FOR YOU! YOU STILL CAN'T SEE THAT!?</font>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Ummm... Noah? What are you talking... <font size=\"3.6\">EEK!</font>\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "What are you doing!? You're drunk! Please calm down!\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "You should've realized for a while now, right? Compare to Helena... I rather... you...\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "No...... <font size=\"3.6\">AHHHHHH!!</font>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>もうすぐ進級テストだね。緊張する……</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "大丈夫だよ。IからJの進級テストはそんなに難しくないって先輩が言ってたよ。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "そんな簡単に……\nそりゃ、AromaとClaraとDanielは3大優等生だから、楽勝だろうけどさ……\nテストの結果が悪かったら、来学期から2組でみんなと別々になっちゃうよ……\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "そんなこと絶対にないよ。Irisなら大丈夫。\n毎日夜遅くまで一緒に頑張ったじゃん。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>うん……</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "余計なことは考えるのやめよ。\n今のIrisの成績なら、いつも通りにテストを受ければ、もし1つや2つケアレスミスしても、1組になれるよ。\n緊張しすぎたら、勉強したこと全部忘れちゃうよ？\nリラックス、リラックス。一緒にJ - 1になろうね。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>うん！Aromaにそう言ってもらって、だいぶ気が楽になった……\nAromaが人前に立つときも、そうやって自分のこと励ませたらいいのにね。\n毎回毎回、こっちが緊張しちゃうよ～あはは！</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "もう！からかわないでよ！\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>Aromaもスターになっちゃうんだもんね。\nなんか急に遠い存在に感じちゃう。\nちょっと寂しいなぁ……\nAromaがスターになっても、私たち友達？</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "大げさだよ……\n何があっても、私たちはずっと友達。\n約束。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>うん！約束だよ！\nもうこんな時間だけど、まだ話してて大丈夫なの？</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "うん。今日、お姉ちゃん帰って来ないんだ。\nでも、そろそろ寝なきゃ。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>うん、私も。\nまた明日、アカデミーでね！おやすみ！</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "おやすみ～\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話終了]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "ふわぁ～チューナー君、目覚ましセットして。\n私、もう寝るね。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[チューナー君]"], "content": "<i>目覚マシをセットしまシタ Aroma オヤスミ！オヤスミ！</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_02", "衝突音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "！？\n何の音……？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……くそ！どいつもこいつもアホばかりだ！</font>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Noahさん……？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "ドアを開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Noahさん……？どうしたの？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "あ……Aromaちゃん……今帰ってきたんだ……\n起こしちゃったかな……？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "ううん。寝ようとしてたとこ……\n大丈夫？顔色が悪いみたい……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "あの年寄りども！素質もないくせに資源だけは一丁前に独り占めしやがって！あんな奴ら消えればいい！\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……Noahさん！？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "この技術がどれだけ重要な物かあいつらは分かっていない！\n科学技術に確変をもたらすことができるんだ！！\nこんなこと！他のやつにはできない！！\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[チューナー君]"], "content": "<i>Noahアルコール量が基準をオーバーしてマス\n休んでクダサイ</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "うるさいな……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["TunerKun_off", "チューナー君OFF"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Aromaちゃん……君は分かるよね？\n僕がどれだけ頑張ってきたか……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "分かるよ。\nNoahさんは、お姉ちゃんのために……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "違う……うわっ！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "image", "attrs": ["aos3201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "わっ！危ないよ、Noahさん。\n座ろう？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">僕は……君のために……</font>\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "え？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">全部君のためなんだよ！\n分からないのか！？</font>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "え……Noahさん……？\n……何言って……<font size=\"3.6\">きゃあ！</font>\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Noahさん！何するの！？\n酔っぱらってるんだよね！？落ち着いて！\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "とっくに気が付いてたんだろう？\nHelenaなんかより……僕は…君のことが……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "いや……<font size=\"3.6\">いやぁ！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>升學考馬上就要到了，好緊張喔……</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "別緊張，實際上 I 升 J 的升學考沒有那麼難喔，聽學姐說的。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>說得倒容易，妳和 Clara、Daniel，三學霸當然輕輕鬆鬆就能考過……要是沒有和你們在同一個級分，下學期就會被分到 2 班去了……</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "才沒那回事啦～Iris 一定也沒問題的。我們每天都一起用功到那麼晚不是嗎？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>嗯……</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "別想那麼多了，以妳現在的成績，只要用平常心去考，即使不小心錯個一、兩題還是會被分到 1 班的喔，太過緊張反而會什麼都記不起來。\n放輕鬆吧～我們都要一起升上 J - 1。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>嗯！聽妳這麼說好令人放心喔……真希望妳也能這樣勉勵台上的自己，每次看妳上台都替妳捏把冷汗呢，哈哈。</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "討厭～別糗我了啦！\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>Aroma 也馬上要成為明星了，好遙遠的感覺，有點寂寞呢……到時候我們還會是朋友嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "沒那麼誇張啦……我保證無論如何我們都是最好的朋友，永遠。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>嗯！說好了喔！\n說起來今天聊得特別晚呢，沒關係嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "今晚姊姊不會回來，所以可以稍微晚一點，不過也差不多要睡了。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>嗯，我也是。那明天學院見囉！晚安。</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "晚安～\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話結束]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "呼哈～喇叭君，設定鬧鐘，我要睡了。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>鬧鐘已設定，Aroma 晚安～晚安～</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_02", "碰撞聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "！？\n什麼聲音……？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……可惡！！一群王八蛋！</font>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Noah……？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Noah？你還好嗎？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "啊……Aroma……我剛到家……\n吵醒妳了嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "不，我正要睡……你沒事嗎？臉色好糟……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "那些老屁股！沒本事又佔著資源！怎麼不去死一死！？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……Noah！？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "他們根本不明白！這項技術的重要性！能夠將科技以一個全新的角度詮釋！！如此重大的突破！難道還有別人做得到嗎！？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>Noah 酒精濃度超標，建議適當休息。</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "少囉唆……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["TunerKun_off", "喇叭君關機"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Aroma……妳懂的吧？我一切的努力……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "我懂的，都是為了姊姊……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "不……唔！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "image", "attrs": ["aos3201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "哇！小心點，先坐下來吧？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">我這一切的努力……都是為了妳呀……</font>\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "咦？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">都是為了妳呀！難道妳還看不出來嗎！？</font>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "呃……Noah？你在說……<font size=\"3.6\">呀！</font>\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "你要做什麼！？你喝醉了！冷靜一點！\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "妳應該也早就察覺了吧？比起 Helena……我對妳……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "不……<font size=\"3.6\">不要！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>곧 진급 시험이구나. 긴장된다...</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "괜찮을 거야. 사실 I에서 J로 진급하는 시험은 그렇게 어렵지 않다고 하던데. 선배한테 들었어.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "말은 쉽지. 너랑 Clara, Daniel 이 세명은 당연히 가볍게 통과하겠지.... 만약 너희와 같은 등급 못 받으면 다음 학기 때 아마 2반으로 배정될 텐데...\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "그런 일은 절대 없을 거야~ Iris라면 할 수 있어. 우리 매일 밤늦게까지 열심히 공부했잖아. 그치?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>응...</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "너무 걱정하지 마. 지금 성적에서 평소처럼 시험 본다면 한 두문제 정도 틀린다 하더라도 안정권이니깐. 너무 긴장하면 오히려 외웠던 것들도 생각이 안 나게 될 수도 있거든.\n그러니깐 긴장 풀고 우리 같이 J - 1로 가자.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>응! 네가 하는 말 들으니깐 조금 편안해졌어... 너도 사람들 앞에  설 때 나한테 한 것처럼 자신감 있게 잘 말할 수 있었으면 좋겠다. 너 앞에서 발표하는 거 볼 때마다 오히려 내 손에 땀이 난다니깐. 하하하.</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "뭐야~! 또 놀리고 있어!\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>Aroma도 이제 연예인이 될 텐데, 뭔가 멀어지는 기분이 들고 외롭고 그렇다... 그때도 우리는 친구일 수 있을까?</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "무슨 말을 그렇게 해...\n누가 뭐라 하더라도 우리 사이는 절대 변하지 않을 거야. 영원히. 약속할게.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>응! 약속한 거다!\n말하다 보니 오늘은 더 늦어버렸네. 괜찮아?</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "응. 오늘 언니도 집에 못 들어 온다 했거든. 그래서 더 얘기할 수 있었어. 그래도 이제 자야 할 시간이긴 하지만.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>응. 나도. \n그럼 내일 아카데미에서 보자. 잘 자.</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "응~ 잘자.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[통화 종료]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "휴우~ 튜너군, 이제 자야 하니깐 알람 좀 설정해줘.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[튜너 군]"], "content": "알람 설정 완료! Aroma 굿나잇~ 굿나잇~\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_02", "부딪히는 소리"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "!?\n무슨 소리지....?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">...제기랄! 멍청한 놈들 같으니라고!</font>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Noah씨...?\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Noah씨.....? 괜찮으세요?\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "아……Aroma……지금 막 집에 왔어……\n나 때문에 깬거니……？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "아니요, 지금 막 자려고 했어요... 괜찮으세요? 안색이 엄청...\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "그 망할 늙은이들! 자격도 능력도 없는 것들이 또 전부 독차지하려고 기를 쓰고 말이야! 어째서 그런 놈들은 일찍 죽어버리지 않는 거지?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……Noah씨!?\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "그놈들은 아무것도 몰라! 이 기술의 중요성을! 분명 과학 기술 역사에  한 획을 그을 수 있을 텐데 말이야!  다른 사람이 할 수 있을 것 같아!?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[튜너 군]"], "content": "Noah의 알코올 농도 기준치 초과! 휴식을 권장함!\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "시끄러워...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["TunerKun_off", "튜너군 OFF"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "...?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "Aroma... 넌 알지? 내가 얼마나 노력했는지...\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "알아요...\n모두 언니를 위해서....\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "아니.... 우욱!\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "image", "attrs": ["aos3201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "앗! 조심하세요. 우선 앉아 계실래요?\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">내가 했던 모든 노력은.... 전부 널 위한 거였어...</font>\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "네?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">널 위해서였다고!\n아직도 모르겠어!?</font>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "아.....Noah씨? \n지금 무슨 얘기를.... <font size=\"3.6\">꺄악!</font>\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "뭐 하시려는 거예요! Noah 씨, 많이 취하셨어요! 진정하세요!\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "너는 진작에 알고 있었잖아?\nHelena보다...내가 더....\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "싫……싫어!!\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>升學考馬上就要到了，好緊張喔……</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "別緊張，實際上 I 升 J 的升學考沒有那麼難喔，聽學姐說的。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>說得倒容易，妳和 Clara、Daniel，三學霸當然輕輕鬆鬆就能考過……要是沒有和你們在同一個級分，下學期就會被分到 2 班去了……</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "才沒那回事啦～Iris 一定也沒問題的。我們每天都一起用功到那麼晚不是嗎？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>嗯……</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "別想那麼多了，以妳現在的成績，只要用平常心去考，即使不小心錯個一、兩題還是會被分到 1 班的喔，太過緊張反而會什麼都記不起來。\n放輕鬆吧～我們都要一起升上 J - 1。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>嗯！聽妳這麼說好令人放心喔……真希望妳也能這樣勉勵台上的自己，每次看妳上台都替妳捏把冷汗呢，哈哈。</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "討厭～別糗我了啦！\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>Aroma 也馬上要成為明星了，好遙遠的感覺，有點寂寞呢……到時候我們還會是朋友嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "沒那麼誇張啦……我保證無論如何我們都是最好的朋友，永遠。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], 