]"], "content": "<i>嗯！听妳这么说好令人放心喔……真希望妳也能这样勉励台上的自己，每次看妳上台都替妳捏把冷汗呢，哈哈。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "讨厌～别糗我了啦！\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>Aroma 也马上要成为明星了，好遥远的感觉，有点寂寞呢……到时候我们还会是朋友吗？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "没那么夸张啦……我保证无论如何我们都是最好的朋友，永远。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>嗯！说好了喔！\n说起来今天聊得特别晚呢，没关系吗？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "今晚姊姊不会回来，所以可以稍微晚一点，不过也差不多要睡了。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Iris]"], "content": "<i>嗯，我也是。那明天学院见啰！晚安。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "晚安～\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通话结束]</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "呼哈～喇叭君，设定闹钟，我要睡了。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>闹钟已设定，Aroma 晚安～晚安～</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_02", "碰撞声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "！ ？\n什么声音……？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……可恶！ ！一群王八蛋！ </font>\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Noah……？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "开门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "Noah？你还好吗？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "啊……Aroma……我刚到家……\n吵醒妳了吗……？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "不，我正要睡……你没事吗？脸色好糟……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "那些老屁股！没本事又占着资源！怎么不去死一死！ ？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Aroma"], "content": "……Noah！ ？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Noah"], "content": "他们根本不明白！这项技术的重要性